   Julia or Python language, even R is supported in
   [https://jupyter.org/]IPython Notebook/Jupyter which can be used to
   give presentations.

LaTeX Beamer

     * [https://bitbucket.org/rivanvx/beamer/wiki/Home]Beamer: Shipped
