       for neuroinformatics.

Open Source

   Open Source is great.

Open Licenses

   Generally, open licenses are part of
     * [http://opendefinition.org/]Open Definition: Read the license
       [http://opendefinition.org/licenses/]here and pick the one you
       like.

Use Licenses

   To choose a license, an easy way is to use
     * [http://choosealicense.com/]Choose a License which helps you decide
       which license to use through several steps.

   CC Licenses can be found at [http://creativecommons.org/]Creative
   Commons. For alternative badges or icons, check the following.
     * [https://github.com/opentf/GuokrBadge]Guokr Badge: Green CC License
       badges. (Documentation is in Chinese.)

